Sentiment Analysis Project

📢 Project Overview
This project focuses on sentiment analysis using Natural Language Processing (NLP). It evaluates the emotional tone of words, sentences, or entire texts, classifying them as positive 😊, negative 😡, or neutral 😐.

🚀 Features

Analyze sentiment in text data 📊

Classify emotions as positive, negative, or neutral 🎭

Utilize machine learning models for better accuracy 🤖

Preprocess text data (tokenization, stemming, lemmatization) 🔍

Visualize sentiment distribution 📈

🛠 Technologies Used

Python 🐍

NLP libraries: NLTK, TextBlob, SpaCy 🧠

Machine Learning: Scikit-Learn, TensorFlow, PyTorch 🏗️

Data Visualization: Matplotlib, Seaborn 🎨
